{
  "texts": [
    "To understand how the models perform on the various types of requests, we perform a detailed request-type-based series of experiments.",
    "These evaluations are measured using GPT-4 to annotate how well the assistant responded on a given scale.",
    "In this section, we discuss these results.",
    "Table 2 aggregates the results of these experiments, and Table 3 highlights these different types of requests.",
    "To assess the limits of how the models can process a procedural plan and navigate through it, we performed a navigation-focused evaluation."
